# 3 step formula.
ASK YOURSELVES:
1.are X & y are numeric?- scatter plot
2. is there a linear relationship between X & y?- scatter plot
3. is there a linear relationship between X & y?- scatter plot with line of best fit

4.is one column a category?- bar chart/count plot

5.want to see the distribution of a distribution?- histogram/box plot/kde plot.


